<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="853">Kew Bull.</emphasis>
4: 285. 1949) referred to material in LINN as &quot;the type specimen&quot;, they did not distinguish between sheets 845.9 and 845.10 (which are evidently not part of the same gathering so Art. 9.15 does not apply).
</paragraph>
